  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2 id=\"h_01HYXRZTTYKHWBDBWQ1BB7B8M0\">Added</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span>Ability to use StartupProbe in LCP</span></li>\n<li><span>Add configuration/history tab and display configuration page. Check our <a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/dxp-cloud/latest/en/platform-services/backup-service/backup-service-overview.html#configuring-the-schedule-via-the-console\">documentations.</a></span></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"h_01HYXRZTTYT9RS6T3J45Q1A1MJ\">Bug Fixes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed project filter is not reset when clicking \"Liferay Cloud\" topbar icon/link</li>\n<li>Fixed Environment Var page - Long text in values input overlaps 'show' icon</li>\n<li>Fixed Environment Badge on /settings/info should redirect to /overview page</li>\n<li>Fixed wrong vpn connection error message (expected <span>\"Connection timeout\" instead \"Connection failure\"</span>)</li>\n<li>Fixed  Services page - Endpoint column overlaps long service image name</li>\n</ul>"
      },
